          SHORT="Volume control utility for PulseAudio"

cat << EOF
PulseAudio Volume Control (pavucontrol) is a simple GTK based volume control tool
("mixer") for the PulseAudio sound server. In contrast to classic mixer tools
this one allows you to control both the volume of hardware devices and of each
playback stream seperately.
EOF
